    "intro": "The Boundaries agreement establishes the safe operating environment for the Northridge Community Center Sandbox. It defines three critical categories: Publication Boundaries govern what information may leave this space; Privacy Boundaries dictate what data may enter it; and Personal Boundaries establish the safeguards necessary to protect the cognitive and emotional well-being of the cohort members undertaking this deeply transformative work."
